Package: montyhall
Title: Monty Hall Simulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Diana",
           family = "York",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
	   email = "dlyork1@asu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The project allows a user to simulate the famous Monty Hall Problem. The user is given the option to play the standard three door game, or try different variations. The goal of this package is to show the best strategy of winning. 
